    "Title": "Investigate Missing Pilot and Cargo",
    "TitleKey": "cfp_missingperson_sabotage_servers_retrievecargo_VH_XT_title_001",
    "Description": "A local courier who has been working for Citizen for Prosperity, ~mission(TargetName), was reported missing earlier this week. We believe that they may have been captured by members of XenoThreat who were after the encrypted data-drives and important cargo they were transporting for us.  \n\nWe would like you to go to ~mission(Location|Address) to ascertain what has happened to ~mission(TargetName|First), destroy any servers which may be housing the stolen data,  and deliver the recovered cargo to ~mission(Destination|Address).\n\nIt's a lot to ask, but I believe you're up to the challenge.\n \nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
    "DescriptionKey": "cfp_missingperson_sabotage_servers_retrievecargo_VH_XT_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "A local courier who has been working for Citizen for Prosperity, [TargetName], was reported missing earlier this week. We believe that they may have been captured by members of XenoThreat who were after the encrypted data-drives and important cargo they were transporting for us.  \n\nWe would like you to go to [Location|Address] to ascertain what has happened to [TargetName|First], destroy any servers which may be housing the stolen data,  and deliver the recovered cargo to [Destination|Address].\n\nIt's a lot to ask, but I believe you're up to the challenge.\n \nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
